Task 3

x1 =rnorm(10)
x2 =rnorm(10)
x1=cbind(x1)
x2=cbind(x2)
X = cbind(x1,x2)
cov_X=(t(X)%*%X)/nrow(X)
w1 =rnorm(10000)
w2 =rnorm(10000)
w1=cbind(w1)
w2=cbind(w2)
W = cbind(w1,w2)
W_cov=(t(W)%*%W)/nrow(W)
A_inv=chol(Sigma_inv)
Y=X%*%A
Y=W%*%A
plot(Y[,2],Y[,1],col=rgb(0, 0, 0, .05))
